# Empty State

## Anatomy

- visual
- headline
- body
- primary action
- secondary action
- optional help link

## States

- first use
- no results
- filtered to empty
- permission-limited empty
- recoverable error masquerading as empty

## Variants

- compact inline
- page-level
- table-level
- card-level

## Tokens

- `--color-muted`
- `--color-foreground`
- `--space-*`
- `--text-*`

## Accessibility

- Do not rely on illustration alone.
- Primary recovery action must be keyboard reachable.
- Empty state copy explains why the state exists and what the user can do.
